request.description:
Return a collection of ProfileObj for the specified account as a JSON object.

Optionally the url can specify one {@link filterBy}="value" query parameter and the ordering is specified in the query parameter order_by="orderby1,orderby2...{@link orderBy}". Navigation through a query result list is done using the {@link pageControls} url query parameters. Optional contents are specified in the query parameter include_list="include1,include2...{@link includeList}".

To filter questions with empty or null answers use keyword NULL e.g. \=NULL OR use EMPTY value e.g. \= NOTE: NULL is a case insensitive keyword and will not filter questions as a text.

request.description:
Add a new profile for the specified account. The ProfileObj is provided in the request body as a JSON object.

Optional url query parameters:

`&profileIdentifier=SYNC_EXTERNAL (External Profile ID) &profileIdentifier=SYNC_EMAIL (Email) &profileIdentifier=SYNC_PIN (username)` Default is 'EXTERNAL'. Used when allowDuplicates=no or creating a new profile.

No Mandatory fields.
